KELLER WILLIAMS ISLAND LIFE REAL ESTATE

data.description: Are you ready to experience Florida's desirable lifestyle?  Then this 3 bedroom, 2 bath cornered lot home is a must see!  Conveniently located within a 1 mile walk/bicycle ride to beautiful Manasota Key Beach and Lemon Bay Preserves (walking trails), this beach vibe ranch style home offers unique options on its split-level plan. The adjacent den can transform the primary room into a dreamy private suite with its own independent side entrance and exit. The primary bedroom also has an adjacent bonus room that can become a nursery, office, or personal gym.  In the kitchen there are new cabinets, quartz countertops, and new whirlpool appliances. The kitchen has sliding door access to an air-conditioned lanai that leads to a fully fenced backyard to let those pets roam freely.  Additional pluses: front porch; 2019 ac and water heater, concrete patio area, outside shower; large shed; and NO HOA fees, furnishing optional and negotiable (see attached available furniture inventory),  Bring your boat or RV and start living the dream!
